  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MOJITO THE CAT </strong></h2>Roll arround with Mojito, a cube-shaped cat and push your space vision to the limit, use the logic to find the shortest path to the exit. <br>Rotate the pieces to reach all coins, get the fish scrape and go to the gate to jump to the next level<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798950/extras/821f6dbe2b1ca0a125166b99b6d434c5.avif?t=1753254702\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br><br>Help Mojito the Cute Cat explore the different worlds, unlock all characterized skins and solve all the puzzles with the few number of movements to get 3 golden cubes in every level<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EASY RULE</strong></h2>Pick all yarn balls and fish scrape and go to the end point. Do it with the least number of moves.<br>Easy starting levels for newbie players<br>Hard ending levels for extreme players<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798950/extras/485ac6a4aa6fa94495ceb110d16eb8cc.poster.avif?t=1753254702\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798950/extras/485ac6a4aa6fa94495ceb110d16eb8cc.webm?t=1753254702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798950/extras/485ac6a4aa6fa94495ceb110d16eb8cc.mp4?t=1753254702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>6 WORLDS 60 LEVELS</strong></h2>Trainning Gardens, Oasis, Woodland, Ice, Volcano & Fantasy<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798950/extras/f9aa505ee66d1dc3b1da8638a14bfa6e.poster.avif?t=1753254702\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"http